Source.Name: yaml-language-server
Source.Description: Supports JSON Schema 7 and below. Starting from 1.0.0 the language server uses eemeli/yaml as the new YAML parser, which strictly enforces the specified YAML spec version. Default YAML spec version is 1.2, it can be changed with yaml.yamlVersion setting.
